<br>
Again, I realize that limiting a guild is limiting options to a degree.  But tactics and planning can overcome a lot of these obstacles, and alliances can overcome a lot more.  Im not so much worried as to limiting hunting/raid options because of the number of good aligned guilds that are in force that make an alliance (or alliances) possible, as I am in creating something that the Firiona Vie Paladin can be proud of (wether guilded or not).<br>
